NLGbAseRedisLoadMetadata - Class in semkit.semanticresources
This method is intended to load NLGbAse Metadata in the REDIS database it uses the jedis jar and the redis base.

Some links to help:
The Github of Redis
The home of Redis

You need an active Redis Server before using this class.

To launch the Redis base under Linux :
launch [yourpath]./redis-server

To launch the Redis base under Windows in 64 bits:
launch [yourpath]\redis-2.4.5-win32-win64\64bit\redis-server.exe

We have tested Redis under Windows.
